[This is another disease that seems to be rampant, and the bats are very affected by this disease. Research has not kept pace with the devastating spread of this disease. The only bright spot is that some bats are becoming immune to its terrible effects.

Prince Edward Island may be located on the HealthMap/ProMED-mail interactive map at: http://healthmap.org/r/5Kc4. - Mod.TG]
